These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Pet: frog, lizard, horse, turtle
House: craftsman, townhouse, ranch-style, victorian
1. Pet:frog is on the right of House:ranch-style##1
2. House:victorian is on the far left##1
3. House:ranch-style is between House:townhouse and Pet:lizard##2
4. Pet:turtle is on the far left##1
5. Pet:horse is between Pet:lizard and Pet:frog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Pet   | turtle         | lizard   | horse | frog       |
| House      | victorian | craftsman | ranch-style   | townhouse |

