.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Beverage: soy-milk, 7up, cola, fanta
Music-Genre: classical, metal, blues, soul
1. Music-Genre:soul is between Beverage:cola and Music-Genre:metal##2
2. Beverage:fanta is on the far right##1
3. Music-Genre:blues is on the right of Music-Genre:classical##1
4. Beverage:soy-milk is on the left of Music-Genre:classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage         | 7up | soy-milk | cola | fanta |
| Music-Genre   | metal    | soul   | classical | blues       |

