.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
Movie-Genre: epic, martial-arts, satire, thriller
Hobby: fishing, baking, hiking, skydiving
1. Hobby:hiking is on the right of Movie-Genre:thriller##1
2. Hobby:hiking is between Hobby:baking and Movie-Genre:martial-arts##2
3. Hobby:baking is on the far left##1
4. Hobby:skydiving is on the left of Movie-Genre:satire##1
5. Movie-Genre:martial-arts == Hobby:skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre          | thriller    | epic | martial-arts   | satire  |
| Hobby   | baking | hiking   | skydiving | fishing |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
