3. Birthday:may is on the far right##1
4. Movie-Genre:time-travel is on the right of Birthday:november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre     | adventure   | time-travel    | drama       | western   |
| Birthday   | november | july | april | may |

